			<p style="text-align:justify; margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-family:&quot;jf-openhuninn-1.1&quot;,sans-serif">亞哈因為「建築」</span><span style="font-family:&quot;jf-openhuninn-1.1&quot;,sans-serif">(</span><span dir="RTL" style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif">בנה</span></span><span style="font-family:&quot;jf-openhuninn-1.1&quot;,sans-serif">)也必啟動古老的先知預言(<a class="article-citation" data-book="11" data-end-chapter="14" data-end-verse="16" data-start-chapter="14" data-start-verse="10" href="javascript:void(0);">王上十四10-16</a>，</span></span></span></span></span><a class="article-citation" data-book="11" data-end-chapter="21" data-end-verse="24" data-start-chapter="21" data-start-verse="21" href="javascript:void(0);">二十一21-24</a><span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-family:&quot;jf-openhuninn-1.1&quot;,sans-serif">)</span></span></span></span></span></p>
			</td>
			<td style="border-bottom:solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-left:none; border-right:solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-top:none; padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; vertical-align:top; width:207.4pt" width="277">
			<p style="text-align:justify; margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-family:&quot;jf-openhuninn-1.1&quot;,sans-serif">希伊勒因為「建築」</span><span style="font-family:&quot;jf-openhuninn-1.1&quot;,sans-serif">(</span><span dir="RTL" style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif">בנה</span></span><span style="font-family:&quot;jf-openhuninn-1.1&quot;,sans-serif">)而啟動了古老的先知預言(<a class="article-citation" data-book="6" data-end-chapter="" data-end-verse="" data-start-chapter="6" data-start-verse="26" href="javascript:void(0);">書六26</a>)。</span></span></span></span></span></p>
			</td>
