		<tr>
			<td style="border-style:solid; border-top:none; border-width:1.0pt; padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; vertical-align:top; width:207.4pt" width="277">
			<p style="text-align:justify; margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-family:&quot;jf-openhuninn-1.1&quot;,sans-serif">先知預言涉及亞哈一人的違反盟約行為。</span></span></span></span></span></p>
			</td>
			<td style="border-bottom:solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-left:none; border-right:solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-top:none; padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; vertical-align:top; width:207.4pt" width="277">
			<p style="text-align:justify; margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-family:&quot;jf-openhuninn-1.1&quot;,sans-serif">這古老的先知預言涉及亞干一人的違反盟約行為。</span></span></span></span></span></p>
			</td>
